    • appointment

      public appointment(int appointmentID, String title, String description, String location, String appointmentType, Timestamp appointmentStart, Timestamp appointmentEnd, Timestamp appointmentCreationDate, String appointmentCreationUser, Timestamp appointmentLastUpdate, String appointmentLastUpdatedBy, int customerID, int userID, int contactID)
      The appointment object. An object containing appointment information.
      Parameters:
      appointmentID - The appointment's ID.
      title - The appointment's title.
      description - The appointment's description.
      location - The location of the appointment.
      appointmentType - The type of appointment.
      appointmentStart - The start time of the appointment.
      appointmentEnd - The end time of the appointment.
      appointmentCreationDate - The time the appointment was created.
      appointmentCreationUser - The user that created the appointment.
      appointmentLastUpdate - The time the appointment was last updated.
      appointmentLastUpdatedBy - The user that last updated the appointment.
      customerID - The customer ID involved with the appointment.
      userID - The user ID involved with the appointment.
      contactID - The contact ID involved with the appointment.
